## Acceptance (auto-verify)
- [ ] Keys follow `{screenId}__{compId}` on interactive widgets
- [ ] Mapping rules from UI_MAPPING_GUIDE.md applied
- [ ] Layout matches `design.json` (placement/widthMode/constraints)
- [ ] Interactions/state/navigation match `spec.md` and plan
- [ ] All contracts satisfied: ARCHITECTURE_CONTRACT.md, PROJECT_CONTRACT.md, TEST_CONTRACT.md
- [ ] All guardrails satisfied (G-01 through G-18)
- [ ] Tests generated per TEST_CONTRACT.md with required coverage
- [ ] Widget-to-test ratio 1:1 verified (G-11)
- [ ] i18n files generated, no hardcoded strings (G-12, G-18)
- [ ] Build fails on any contract/guardrail violation